692c73c8ad6a68ee0e","tid":861064,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5cb7157f83a211680efac93e007308aa871af40","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"27e4e26231fe3a358009caa25d63cbfc1ec71e28","tid":861064,"uid":203365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:54:14.000Z","msg":"Reading 6<br />\nListening 6<br />\nWriting 5<br />\nSpeaking 5.5<br />\nOverall 5.5<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法上到6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T20:00:56.000Z","msg":"你有幾多時間預備下次ielts？<br />\n定係打擊太大，純粹係改善英文？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T22:35:50.000Z","msg":"師兄勁喎, 我都要考ielts, 上次考7分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要考到8分。 writing 特別廢得6分,點升grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd0586e2da1aa519e54c4d0a0ea9809977c90fe","tid":861064,"uid":199529,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:08:32.000Z","msg":"Listening 同 reading 操多D就會升到分，而兩份卷係用黎拉高個overall band。<br />\nWriting 可以睇下ieltsliz嘅教學同埋睇多D sample essays。<br />\nSpeaking 盡量講多D，唔好問一句答一句，考前可以google果個月出過嘅題目，你可以大概唸下有咩可以講。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f671c6d129fcc7c272bcf93eed6a4e38b9fc3c5","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"528e996bcff3f48187526db45ed32d121aa46d7b","tid":861064,"uid":203365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5cb7157f83a211680efac93e007308aa871af40","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"27e4e26231fe3a358009caa25d63cbfc1ec71e28","tid":861064,"uid":203365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:54:14.000Z","msg":"Reading 6<br />\nListening 6<br />\nWriting 5<br />\nSpeaking 5.5<br />\nOverall 5.5<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法上到6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T20:00:56.000Z","msg":"你有幾多時間預備下次ielts？<br />\n定係打擊太大，純粹係改善英文？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T20:17:35.000Z","msg":"我下年6月前考到6.5分就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> DSE得2 今次考ielts做左Cambridge6-9 paper 但都得5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">既然仲有8個月，你應該打返好個底先<br />\n最後1-2個月先操paper</span><br />\n<br />\n你唔打好個底，死操難操成績都只會差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學外語，最重要產生語感。換句話講，你要日日浸，當自己生活係英語環境<br />\n<br />\n有覺悟就拉落下面繼續睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 出街唔好聽歌，要聽podcast (講得太快唔緊要，聽聽下就會慣）</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人普遍忽略podcast依個免費正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  podcast 上面，有好多免費得意野聽<br />\n<br />\n個人習慣聽BBC 出啲podcast，順便練英國口音<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 空閒時睇劇集/ 戲，最好down落黎有中英雙字幕嗰款</strong><br />\n<br />\n開頭1-2個月睇中文字幕，睇劇上癮之後就間唔中望下英文字幕<br />\n<br />\n最高境界係只睇英文字幕，甚至無字幕。不過唔洗迫自己去到最高境界。<br />\n<br />\n睇得多，listening, speaking, reading 都會得心應手。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 好多人反對背word list，不過你reading 低分反映左你詞彙非常貧乏。唔好怕瘀，拿拿臨跑去書局擦本方便帶出街嘅 word list （即係台灣出嗰啲乜乜乜 必學300單詞 類嘅書)</strong><br />\n<br />\n買完限自己每日背少少，1-2個月背好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 背完word list，去書局揀本自己有興趣嘅青少年英文小說煲</strong><br />\n<br />\n睇睇下你grammar會不知不覺突飛猛進，從而改善writing, reading。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得game of thrones 唔錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 最後1-2個月，操paper。 另外上網搵model band 9 essay 瘋狂手抄。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>6. 決心。無決心只會半途而廢。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好只求考ielts過關。升到上asso/ degree、甚至出黎做野，英文好會令你易吸收，甚至多咗自信心。<br />\n<br />\n學好英文，你會發覺依個世界原來好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我仍然追求緊更上乘嘅英語能力，目標係native speaker程度，一齊加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d52f9414c6cb094cec2eb8c7801d2ab9a88b3c1","tid":861064,"uid":72046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:22:25.000Z","msg":"R5.0<br />\nL5.0<br />\nW5.5<br />\nO 5.5<br />\nOverall 5.5<br />\n我都想上6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adf207202827dc80260cdbba5829cfa63d94ce9","tid":861064,"uid":203365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f671c6d129fcc7c272bcf93eed6a4e38b9fc3c5","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"528e996bcff3f48187526db45ed32d121aa46d7b","tid":861064,"uid":203365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5cb7157f83a211680efac93e007308aa871af40","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":3,"dislike":76,"score":-73,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T20:00:56.000Z","msg":"你有幾多時間預備下次ielts？<br />\n定係打擊太大，純粹係改善英文？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T20:17:35.000Z","msg":"我下年6月前考到6.5分就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> DSE得2 今次考ielts做左Cambridge6-9 paper 但都得5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">既然仲有8個月，你應該打返好個底先<br />\n最後1-2個月先操paper</span><br />\n<br />\n你唔打好個底，死操難操成績都只會差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學外語，最重要產生語感。換句話講，你要日日浸，當自己生活係英語環境<br />\n<br />\n有覺悟就拉落下面繼續睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 出街唔好聽歌，要聽podcast (講得太快唔緊要，聽聽下就會慣）</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人普遍忽略podcast依個免費正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  podcast 上面，有好多免費得意野聽<br />\n<br />\n個人習慣聽BBC 出啲podcast，順便練英國口音<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 空閒時睇劇集/ 戲，最好down落黎有中英雙字幕嗰款</strong><br />\n<br />\n開頭1-2個月睇中文字幕，睇劇上癮之後就間唔中望下英文字幕<br />\n<br />\n最高境界係只睇英文字幕，甚至無字幕。不過唔洗迫自己去到最高境界。<br />\n<br />\n睇得多，listening, speaking, reading 都會得心應手。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 好多人反對背word list，不過你reading 低分反映左你詞彙非常貧乏。唔好怕瘀，拿拿臨跑去書局擦本方便帶出街嘅 word list （即係台灣出嗰啲乜乜乜 必學300單詞 類嘅書)</strong><br />\n<br />\n買完限自己每日背少少，1-2個月背好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 背完word list，去書局揀本自己有興趣嘅青少年英文小說煲</strong><br />\n<br />\n睇睇下你grammar會不知不覺突飛猛進，從而改善writing, reading。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得game of thrones 唔錯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5. 最後1-2個月，操paper。 另外上網搵model band 9 essay 瘋狂手抄。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>6. 決心。無決心只會半途而廢。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好只求考ielts過關。升到上asso/ degree、甚至出黎做野，英文好會令你易吸收，甚至多咗自信心。<br />\n<br />\n學好英文，你會發覺依個世界原來好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我仍然追求緊更上乘嘅英語能力，目標係native speaker程度，一齊加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"畢生受用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90fbd16469cf8a58e9687aad98099b446fbe0f3","tid":861064,"uid":206115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"考多次"},{"pid":"6ec006ed51d56114eb85f71fcc0b524434f17b24","tid":861064,"uid":77948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"DSE英文得3<br />\n分卷4334<br />\n如果咁既底考ielts 會大概幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f690c71e8e5149be26d63105ca415334703b52","tid":861064,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ec006ed51d56114eb85f71fcc0b524434f1