<br />\n<br />\n唔好只求考ielts過關。升到上asso/ degree、甚至出黎做野，英文好會令你易吸收，甚至多咗自信心。<br />\n<br />\n學好英文，你會發覺依個世界原來好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我仍然追求緊更上乘嘅英語能力，目標係native speaker程度，一齊加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"聽bbc啲podcast有冇字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"英劇有冇咩推薦 暫時睇左inside no.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2210b60c24e8186b9ad75377318a9aa4c6d11ff0","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b333af014a07398bef6c40b9ab2cf2bbafc2fb9","tid":861064,"uid":202538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3cb080d458244a409c88add70f8ff1926996845","tid":861064,"uid":198729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbba19f0f1595931064e2d3ad2b85b7745a08acd","tid":861064,"uid":202538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"聽bbc啲podcast有冇字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"英劇有冇咩推薦 暫時睇左inside no.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"我反而睇美劇多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nModern Family<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}